snippet.title: Sky Arena Early Access Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
BUY THE GAME ON STEAM EARLY ACCESS
http://store.steampowered.com/app/309900

Sky Arena is a modern re-imagination of the Starfox multiplayer mode. You pilot a jet fighter to have fast paced dogfights against three of your friends. Play either locally, in splitscreen mode, or create an online game and let your friends join from all over the world.

TWITTER: twitter.com/skyarenagame
FACEBOOK: facebook.com/skyarenagame
REDDIT: reddit.com/r/skyarenagame
